Nathan Williams (born 5 October 1983) is a Welsh rugby union player. A prop forward, he is a Wales Under-21 international.
Williams played for the Scarlets, Llanelli, Narberth and Moseley. In May 2011 he joined the Newport Gwent Dragons regional team.
